407
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:20,970
Chief Shen,

408
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:22,230
we must have displeased

409
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,070
Tuo God.

410
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:26,690
That voice...

411
00:21:27,660 --> 00:21:28,350
Tuo God,

412
00:21:28,380 --> 00:21:29,750
