Tuo God is here.

463
00:24:28,610 --> 00:24:29,200
Tuo God!

464
00:24:29,330 --> 00:24:30,010
Hurry up.

465
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:31,070
Have a look at Tuo God.

466
00:24:31,730 --> 00:24:32,610
Tuo God is here.

467
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:33,920
Let's go.

