535
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:56,840
Zeng Sanyi.

536
00:26:57,860 --> 00:27:00,100
Greetings, Administrator Gu,

537
00:27:00,580 --> 00:27:01,360
Minister Zeng.

538
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:02,950
